00:02:13.130 --> 00:02:14.426
BRENDON AYANBADEJO: He was.

00:02:14.426 --> 00:02:16.306
He was a linebacker, he was.

00:02:19.080 --> 00:02:20.990
FEMALE SPEAKER: Brendon also
