constitutional amendment

00:04:55.740 --> 00:04:58.320
in Minnesota that was going
to ban same sex marriage.

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:00.990
And I said, yeah, that seems
like a great thing to do.

00:05:00.990 --> 00:05:02.550
I don't think anyone should
be banned from

00:05:02.550 --> 00:05:03.590
