00:05:12.630 --> 00:05:17.660
And it made me really upset,
because it was a First

00:05:17.660 --> 00:05:21.420
Amendment violation from elected
US Representative.

00:05:21.420 --> 00:05:25.050
And it was also the fact
that, why do you care?

00:05:25.050 --> 00:05:27.420
What does it matter to you if
two people who love each other

00:05:27.420 --> 00:05:28.150
want to get married.

00:05:28.150 --> 00:05:29.990
That doesn't affect your
life in the slightest.

00:05:29.990 --> 00:05:32.960
And so I wrote a letter back,
which, then, Deadspin

00:05:32.960 --> 00:05:34.872
published, and a lot
of people saw.

00:05:34.872 --> 00:05:36.080
[LAUGHTER]

00:05:36.080 --> 00:05:39.940
CHRIS KLUWE: And then it kind of
broadened the platform that

00:05:39.940 --> 00:05:43.170
I was able to speak on,
