you have to have empathy.

00:05:54.520 --> 00:05:56.130
You have to treat people the
way you would want to be

00:05:56.130 --> 00:05:59.140
treated in order to have a
functional society, so that's

00:05:59.140 --> 00:05:59.590
how I got involved.

00:05:59.590 --> 00:06:02.894
[APPLAUSE]

00:06:02.894 --> 00:06:04.790
