felt about that.

00:22:12.200 --> 00:22:14.103
BRENDON AYANBADEJO: Yeah,
Robbie Rogers, as well.

00:22:14.103 --> 00:22:14.970
FEMALE SPEAKER: Yes.

00:22:14.970 --> 00:22:16.410
BRENDON AYANBADEJO: I, just,
think it's so amazing.

00:22:16.410 --> 00:22:24.820
And also there's something that,
