00:24:52.170 --> 00:24:56.800
view any sort of speaking out
or attention as distraction.

00:24:56.800 --> 00:24:58.490
And I don't think that
that's the case.

00:24:58.490 --> 00:25:00.820
I think that you can be a
professional athlete, you can

00:25:00.820 --> 00:25:03.500
play at a very high level, and
you can also raise awareness

00:25:03.500 --> 00:25:06.650
for very important issues that
affect a large amount of

00:25:06.650 --> 00:25:08.180
people in this country.

00:25:08.180 --> 00:25:10.530
You know, you hear about all
these guys who have either

00:25:10.530 --> 00:25:13.420
their charities or they have
their events or they're doing

00:25:13.420 --> 00:25:16.000
fundraising for the NFL or
awareness for the NFL.

00:25:16.000 --> 00:25:18.450
Well those are exactly
