00:42:34.540 --> 00:42:35.550
better coach.

00:42:35.550 --> 00:42:39.480
I guess he's spoken in New
York, and he's one of the

00:42:39.480 --> 00:42:42.650
assistant athletic people, I
think, for the softball team

00:42:42.650 --> 00:42:43.200
at Rutgers.

00:42:43.200 --> 00:42:46.480
So he is well familiar with
the whole bullying thing.

00:42:46.480 --> 00:42:51.660
