00:49:34.240 --> 00:49:36.180
There's education that
needs to take place.

00:49:36.180 --> 00:49:38.800
A conversation needs to take
place, and that's what we're

00:49:38.800 --> 00:49:40.950
here to do, and that's
what we're doing.

00:49:40.950 --> 00:49:42.670
But we have a long
ways to go, so we

00:49:42.670 --> 00:49:43.890
just continue to educate.

00:49:43.890 --> 00:49:45.660
And there are a lot of athletes
